Project: CTO Map — 52-week Technical CTO curriculum tracker
Stack: Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Prisma/SQLite, Tailwind CSS (dark mode)

RULES:
- ALL UI needs dark mode (dark: Tailwind classes on every element)
- ALL buttons/links need min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px]
- Client components: add 'use client'; at top
- Use existing contexts: useToast(), useProgress(), useTheme()
- /api/task-items returns { learn: [], build: [] } NOT flat array
- After TaskItem changes → calculateDayCompletion() → update Day → check Week
- Use useRef for callback props (prevents infinite loops)
- npm install --legacy-peer-deps
- Types: lib/types.ts | Validators: lib/validators.ts
- CSS utilities: .card, .stat-card, .badge-blue, .badge-green, .skeleton
